Gas lighters are masters at manipulation. They professionally deflect all attention from themselves back to you in a way that leaves you wondering what happened, repeatedly, causing you to believe youâ€™re going crazy. It is psychological and emotional abuse, without a doubt. They will corner you with their constant back handed comments, name calling, mocking, and insulting and derogatory shots continuously fired at you, and when you dare to defend yourself by speaking up or disagreeing with them it can often turn into a yelling match, by their design, that leaves them laughing at you and accusing you of being abusive. Itâ€™s manipulation 101, once youâ€™re able to see it. Now my 12y/o daughter is feeling it from her too. These narcissistic gas lighters have no remorse or conscience.
